WEBVTT

00:01:43.438 --> 00:01:47.150
Kitu kinakuja. Kitu chenye njaa ya damu.

00:01:47.233 --> 00:01:51.821
Kivuli kinakua ukutani nyuma yako, kikikumeza gizani.

00:01:51.904 --> 00:01:53.865
-Karibu imefika. -Ni nini?

00:01:53.948 --> 00:01:55.283
Vipi kama ni Demogorgon?

00:01:55.366 --> 00:01:58.411
Ee Yesu, tumechanganyikiwa sana ikiwa ni Demogorgon.

00:01:58.494 --> 00:01:59.537
Sio Demogorgon.

00:01:59.621 --> 00:02:01.873
Jeshi la trogloditi linaingia ndani ya chumba!

00:02:01.956 --> 00:02:04.083
- Trogloditi? - Nilikuambia.

00:02:07.545 --> 00:02:08.963
Subiri kidogo.

00:02:09.631 --> 00:02:11.591
Umesikia hilo?

00:02:11.674 --> 00:02:13.092
Hiyo... sauti hiyo?

00:02:13.176 --> 00:02:15.845
Boom... boom...

00:02:15.928 --> 00:02:17.680
- Boom!

00:02:17.764 --> 00:02:19.641
Hilo halikutoka kwa troglodytes. Hapana, hilo...

00:02:19.724 --> 00:02:21.392
Hilo lilitokana na kitu kingine.

00:02:23.853 --> 00:02:25.855
- Demogorgon!

00:02:25.938 --> 00:02:27.398
-Tuko katika hali mbaya sana. -Will, kitendo chako!

00:02:27.482 --> 00:02:28.775
-Sijui! -Mshambulie!

00:02:28.858 --> 00:02:30.151
Ningelazimika kuzungusha 13 au zaidi!

00:02:30.234 --> 00:02:32.070
Hatari sana. Tengeneza uchawi wa kujilinda.

00:02:32.153 --> 00:02:34.697
-Usiwe mjanja. Mshambulie! -Ulinzi wa Wachezaji.

00:02:34.781 --> 00:02:37.492
Demogorgon amechoka na ugomvi wako wa kipumbavu wa kibinadamu!

00:02:37.575 --> 00:02:39.369
Inakukanyaga.

00:02:39.452 --> 00:02:40.453
-Boom! -Mpige moto!

00:02:40.536 --> 00:02:42.830
-Kukanyaga kwingine, boom! -Ulinzi wa Wachezaji.

00:02:42.914 --> 00:02:45.750
- Ananguruma kwa hasira!

00:02:45.833 --> 00:02:47.335
- Mpira wa Moto!

00:02:47.418 --> 00:02:49.045
- Loo, shit! - Ilienda wapi?

00:02:49.128 --> 00:02:50.838
- Iko wapi? - Sijui!

00:02:50.922 --> 00:02:52.465
- Je, ni 13? - Sijui!

00:02:52.548 --> 00:02:53.716
- Iko wapi? - Ee Mungu wangu!

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:55.385
- Mike! - Ee Mungu wangu! Ee Mungu wangu!

00:02:55.468 --> 00:02:56.552
- Mike! - Je, unaweza kuipata bado?

00:02:56.636 --> 00:02:57.720
Hapana, siwezi kuipata!

00:02:57.804 --> 00:02:59.472
- Mike! - Ee Mungu wangu! Ee Mungu wangu!

00:02:59.555 --> 00:03:01.349
Mama, tuko katikati ya kampeni!

00:03:01.432 --> 00:03:03.559
Unamaanisha mwisho? Kumi na tano baadaye.

00:03:03.643 --> 00:03:06.813
- Mungu wangu! Mpumbavu wa ajabu! - Kwa nini tunapaswa kwenda?

00:03:06.938 --> 00:03:09.607
-Mama, subiri, dakika 20 tu zaidi! -Ni usiku wa shule, Michael.

00:03:09.690 --> 00:03:12.151
Nimemlaza Holly kitandani. Unaweza kumaliza wikendi ijayo.

00:03:12.235 --> 00:03:13.778
-Lakini hiyo itaharibu mtiririko! -Michael--

00:03:13.861 --> 00:03:15.113
Niko makini, Mama.

00:03:15.196 --> 00:03:17.657
Kampeni ilichukua wiki mbili kupanga.

00:03:17.740 --> 00:03:19.659
Nilipaswa kujuaje kwamba itachukua saa kumi?

00:03:19.742 --> 00:03:21.619
Umekuwa ukicheza kwa saa kumi?

00:03:22.954 --> 00:03:26.749
-Baba, usifikiri kwamba 20 zaidi -- -Nadhani unapaswa kumsikiliza mama yako.

00:03:26.833 --> 00:03:30.294
--Kipande cha takataka kijinga.

00:03:31.337 --> 00:03:33.297
Loo, nimeelewa!

00:03:33.381 --> 00:03:35.258
-Je, saba zinahesabiwa? -Ilikuwa saba?

00:03:35.925 --> 00:03:38.469
Je, Mike aliiona? Basi haihesabiki.

00:03:43.099 --> 00:03:44.267
Enyi, jamani.

00:03:44.350 --> 00:03:46.227
- Je, kuna mtu yeyote anayetaka hii? - Hapana.

00:03:49.689 --> 00:03:50.857
Ndiyo.

00:03:51.649 --> 00:03:53.234
Hapana, sidhani kama...

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:55.945
Ndiyo, yeye ni mrembo.

00:03:56.028 --> 00:03:59.365
Barb, hapana, sidhani hivyo.

00:03:59.449 --> 00:04:00.908
-Barb, wewe si -- -Habari, Nancy.

00:04:01.784 --> 00:04:03.161
Kuna kipande kilichobaki ikiwa unataka.

00:04:03.244 --> 00:04:05.580
-Soseji na pepperoni! -Subiri.

00:04:12.462 --> 00:04:16.382
-Kuna tatizo na dada yako. -Unazungumzia nini?

00:04:16.466 --> 00:04:18.259
- Ana fimbo kwenye makalio yake. - Ndiyo.

00:04:18.342 --> 00:04:20.845
Ni kwa sababu amekuwa akichumbiana na Steve Harrington, mchumba wake wa kimapenzi.

00:04:20.928 --> 00:04:22.680
Ndiyo, anageuka kuwa mjinga kweli.

00:04:22.764 --> 00:04:24.098
Amekuwa mjinga kweli siku zote.

00:04:24.182 --> 00:04:26.058
Hahaa, alikuwa mtulivu.

00:04:26.142 --> 00:04:28.519
Kama wakati huo alivaa kama elf kwa ajili ya kampeni yetu ya mti wa Mzee.

00:04:28.603 --> 00:04:29.812
Miaka minne iliyopita!

00:04:29.937 --> 00:04:31.355
- Nikisema tu. - Baadaye.

00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:34.984
-Ilikuwa saba. -Huh?

00:04:35.067 --> 00:04:36.819
Roli, ilikuwa saba.

00:04:37.904 --> 00:04:40.114
Demogorgon, ilinivutia.

00:04:41.491 --> 00:04:43.159
Tutaonana kesho.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:01.844
- Usiku mwema, wanawake. - Busu usiku wa mama yako kwa ajili yangu.

00:05:03.179 --> 00:05:05.264
Unataka urudi kwangu? Mshindi atapata katuni.

00:05:05.348 --> 00:05:07.016
-Je, kuna katuni yoyote? -Ndiyo.

00:05:07.892 --> 00:05:10.019
Hujambo! Hujambo!

00:05:10.102 --> 00:05:12.063
Sikusema "nenda"!

00:05:14.106 --> 00:05:16.150
Rudi hapa!

00:05:16.234 --> 00:05:18.361
Nitakuua!

00:05:18.444 --> 00:05:20.863
Nitachukua X-Men 134 yako!

00:05:27.161 --> 00:05:28.704
Mwana wa mbwa mwitu.

00:06:27.763 --> 00:06:29.140
Mama?

00:06:29.223 --> 00:06:31.767
- Jonathan? Mama?

00:06:53.706 --> 00:06:56.417
- Habari? Habari?

00:09:29.111 --> 00:09:31.405
Na ndivyo ilivyo kwa Kituo cha Habari asubuhi ya leo.

00:09:31.489 --> 00:09:32.823
Asante kwa kujiunga nasi.

00:09:32.907 --> 00:09:35.201
Hebu tumpe Liz kwenye dawati la habari sasa.

00:09:35.284 --> 00:09:36.702
Sawa, asante, Donna.

00:09:36.786 --> 00:09:37.870
Sasa tuangalie habari za ndani,

00:09:37.953 --> 00:09:41.373
Tunapokea ripoti za kuongezeka kwa umeme na kukatika kwa umeme kote katika kaunti.

00:09:41.457 --> 00:09:44.418
Jana usiku, mamia ya nyumba huko East Hawkins ziliathiriwa,

00:09:44.502 --> 00:09:46.879
na kuwaacha wakazi wengi gizani.

00:09:46.962 --> 00:09:49.090
Chanzo cha kukatika kwa umeme bado hakijajulikana.

00:09:49.173 --> 00:09:51.383
Tuliwasiliana na Maji na Umeme wa Kaunti ya Roane,

00:09:51.467 --> 00:09:54.011
na msemaji anasema kwamba wanajiamini

00:09:54.095 --> 00:09:56.680
umeme utarejeshwa kwenye nyumba zote zilizobaki

00:09:56.764 --> 00:09:58.307
ndani ya saa kadhaa zijazo.

00:10:24.875 --> 00:10:26.043
Mmmh.

00:10:57.491 --> 00:10:59.702
Katika habari nyingine, unaweza kutaka kukaa nyumbani usiku wa leo

00:10:59.785 --> 00:11:01.078
au angalau pakia mwavuli.

00:11:01.162 --> 00:11:03.581
Tunamgeukia mtu anayependa zaidi kuhusu hali ya hewa ya asubuhi, Charles.

00:11:08.085 --> 00:11:10.087
Wako wapi jamani?

00:11:10.171 --> 00:11:12.590
-Jonathan? -Angalia kochi!

00:11:12.673 --> 00:11:13.799
Ugh, nilifanya hivyo.

00:11:14.925 --> 00:11:17.386
Loo... Nimezipata.

00:11:18.512 --> 00:11:20.848
Sawa, mpenzi, tutaonana usiku wa leo.

00:11:20.931 --> 00:11:22.766
-Ndiyo, tutaonana baadaye. -Will yuko wapi?

00:11:22.850 --> 00:11:23.934
Loo, sikumfufua bado.

00:11:24.018 --> 00:11:25.144
- Labda bado amelala.

00:11:25.227 --> 00:11:28.355
-Jonathan, lazima uhakikishe ameamka! -Mama, ninaandaa kifungua kinywa.

00:11:28.439 --> 00:11:30.274
Nilikuambia hili mara elfu.

00:11:30.357 --> 00:11:33.986
Will! Njoo, mpenzi. Ni wakati wa kuamka.

00:11:37.364 --> 00:11:40.743
-Alikuja nyumbani jana usiku, sivyo? -Hayupo chumbani mwake?

00:11:40.826 --> 00:11:43.120
-Je, alirudi nyumbani au la? -Sijui.

00:11:43.203 --> 00:11:44.455
-Hujui? -Hapana.

00:11:44.538 --> 00:11:46.582
Nilifika nyumbani nikiwa nimechelewa. Nilikuwa kazini.

00:11:46.665 --> 00:11:47.708
Ulikuwa unafanya kazi?

00:11:47.791 --> 00:11:49.710
Eric aliniuliza kama ningeweza kujificha. Nikasema ndio.

00:11:49.793 --> 00:11:51.253
Nilidhani tu tunaweza kutumia pesa za ziada.

00:11:51.337 --> 00:11:54.048
-Jonathan, tumezungumzia hili. -Najua, najua.

00:11:54.131 --> 00:11:56.050
Huwezi kuchukua zamu ninapokuwa kazini.

00:11:56.133 --> 00:11:58.302
Mama, si jambo kubwa. Tazama, alikuwa kwenye Wheelers siku nzima.

00:11:58.385 --> 00:12:01.055
- Nina uhakika alibaki tu. - Siwezi kukuamini.

00:12:01.138 --> 00:12:03.724
Siwezi kukuamini wakati mwingine.

00:12:06.810 --> 00:12:10.272
--Hilo ni jambo la kuchukiza.

00:12:10.356 --> 00:12:12.566
- Unachukiza! - Habari?

00:12:12.650 --> 00:12:14.401
Hujambo, Karen. Ni Joyce.

00:12:14.485 --> 00:12:16.528
- Loo, Joyce, habari. - Vipi, Mike?

00:12:16.612 --> 00:12:17.780
- Hujambo! - Kimya!

00:12:17.863 --> 00:12:19.573
-Lugha. -Unatania?

00:12:19.657 --> 00:12:21.033
Je, hiyo ndiyo niliyosikia Will huko nyuma?

00:12:21.116 --> 00:12:22.618
Je,? Hapana, hapana, hapana, ni Mike tu.

00:12:22.701 --> 00:12:24.119
Will hakulala usiku?

00:12:24.203 --> 00:12:26.622
Hapana, aliondoka hapa kidogo baada ya saa 2:00.

00:12:26.705 --> 00:12:28.040
Kwa nini? Hayupo nyumbani?

00:12:28.123 --> 00:12:31.961
Um, unajua nini? Nadhani aliondoka mapema tu kwa... kwenda shuleni.

00:12:32.044 --> 00:12:34.046
-Asante sana. Kwaheri. -Sawa. Kwaheri.

00:12:56.110 --> 00:12:58.904
Hilo ni jambo la ajabu. Simwonei.

00:12:58.988 --> 00:13:00.531
Nakwambia, mama yake yuko sahihi.

00:13:00.614 --> 00:13:02.449
Huenda alienda darasani mapema tena.

00:13:02.533 --> 00:13:05.035
Ndiyo, yeye huwa na wasiwasi kila wakati. Gursky atampa jaribio lingine la pop.

00:13:05.119 --> 00:13:07.037
Inuka moja kwa moja, mabibi na mabwana.

00:13:07.871 --> 00:13:10.374
Inuka moja kwa moja na upate tiketi zako za onyesho la ajabu.

00:13:10.457 --> 00:13:13.085
Unafikiri ni nani angepata pesa zaidi katika onyesho la ajabu?

00:13:14.837 --> 00:13:18.757
Usiku wa manane, Frogface, au Toothless?

00:13:22.511 --> 00:13:24.346
Ningependelea kutumia Toothless.

00:13:24.430 --> 00:13:27.891
Nilikuambia mara milioni, meno yangu yanaingia.

00:13:27.975 --> 00:13:29.727
Inaitwa dysplasia ya cleidocranial.

00:13:29.810 --> 00:13:31.812
"Nilikuambia mara milioni."

00:13:31.895 --> 00:13:33.939
--Fanya kazi ya mkono.

00:13:34.732 --> 00:13:36.066
Fanya hivyo, mjinga!

00:13:42.406 --> 00:13:44.658
Mungu, inanipata kila wakati.

00:13:45.951 --> 00:13:48.829
- Pumbavu. - Nadhani ni vizuri kidogo.

00:13:48.912 --> 00:13:51.081
Ni kama una nguvu kubwa au kitu kama hicho.

00:13:51.165 --> 00:13:53.042
Kama Bw. Ajabu.

00:13:53.125 --> 00:13:55.377
Ndiyo, isipokuwa siwezi kupambana na uovu nayo.

00:14:03.677 --> 00:14:05.512
Kwa hivyo, alipiga simu?

00:14:05.596 --> 00:14:08.140
Punguza sauti yako.

00:14:08.223 --> 00:14:09.808
Je, alifanya hivyo?

00:14:09.892 --> 00:14:11.643
Nilikuambia, sivyo ilivyo.

00:14:12.227 --> 00:14:15.981
Sawa, namaanisha, ndiyo, ananipenda, lakini si hivyo.

00:14:16.690 --> 00:14:17.983
Sisi tu...

00:14:19.109 --> 00:14:20.611
imetengenezwa mara kadhaa.

00:14:20.694 --> 00:14:24.073
"Tumekutana mara kadhaa tu."

00:14:24.156 --> 00:14:25.491
Nance, kwa uzito,

00:14:25.574 --> 00:14:27.659
Utakuwa mzuri sana sasa, ni ujinga.

00:14:27.743 --> 00:14:29.161
Hapana, mimi si.

00:14:29.244 --> 00:14:32.915
Afadhali uendelee kukaa nami, ndivyo ninavyosema.

00:14:32.998 --> 00:14:35.793
Ukiwa rafiki na Tommy H. au Carol--

00:14:35.876 --> 00:14:37.169
Loo, hilo ni jambo baya sana!

00:14:37.252 --> 00:14:39.421
Sawa, nakwambia, ilikuwa mara moja tu...

00:14:40.255 --> 00:14:42.341
- Jambo la mara mbili.

00:14:47.179 --> 00:14:48.472
Ulikuwa unasema?

00:14:58.899 --> 00:15:00.359
-Steve... -Mmm-hmm?

00:15:00.442 --> 00:15:02.111
-Lazima niondoke. -Baada ya dakika moja.

00:15:03.570 --> 00:15:05.864
Steve. Kwa kweli, napenda...

00:15:05.948 --> 00:15:07.783
Kwa kweli, lazima niende.

00:15:07.866 --> 00:15:09.243
Subiri, subiri, subiri. Hebu...

00:15:09.326 --> 00:15:11.203
Njoo, tufanye jambo usiku wa leo, sivyo?

00:15:11.286 --> 00:15:14.206
Uh... Hapana, siwezi. Lazima nisome kwa ajili ya mtihani wa Kaminsky.

00:15:14.289 --> 00:15:16.542
Haya, njoo. GPA yako ni ngapi tena? 3.999...

00:15:16.625 --> 00:15:18.335
Vipimo vya Kaminsky haviwezekani.

00:15:18.419 --> 00:15:20.587
-Sawa, basi, acha nikusaidie. -Umeshindwa kemia.

00:15:20.671 --> 00:15:22.673
-C-minus. -Naam, katika hali hiyo...

00:15:22.756 --> 00:15:25.092
Kwa hivyo nitakuwa hapa, tuseme, kama, saa 8:00?

00:15:25.175 --> 00:15:28.137
-Una kichaa? Mama yangu hangefanya hivyo -- -Nitapanda kupitia dirisha lako.

00:15:28.220 --> 00:15:30.389
Hatajua hata kama nipo. Mimi ni mjanja, kama ninja.

00:15:30.472 --> 00:15:31.723
Wewe ni mwendawazimu.

00:15:31.807 --> 00:15:33.642
Subiri, subiri, subiri. Tu... Sawa, sahau hilo.

00:15:33.725 --> 00:15:35.018
Tunaweza tu...

00:15:35.102 --> 00:15:37.020
Tunaweza tu, kama, kupumzika ndani ya gari langu.

00:15:37.104 --> 00:15:40.065
Tunaweza kupata sehemu nzuri tulivu ya kuegesha magari, na...

00:15:40.149 --> 00:15:43.569
Steve... Lazima nisome.

00:15:43.652 --> 00:15:45.362
Sitanii.

00:15:45.446 --> 00:15:47.739
Naam, unafikiri kwa nini nataka iwe nzuri na tulivu?

00:15:49.616 --> 00:15:51.493
Wewe ni mjinga, Steve Harrington.

00:15:57.458 --> 00:16:00.043
Tukutane Dearborn na Maple saa 2:00.

00:16:00.878 --> 00:16:02.254
Kusoma.

00:16:15.476 --> 00:16:16.768
Vizuri kwako kuonyesha.

00:16:16.852 --> 00:16:20.522
Loo, asubuhi, Flo. Asubuhi, kila mtu.

00:16:20.606 --> 00:16:24.276
-Haya, Mkuu. -Laana! Unaonekana kama kuzimu, Mkuu.

00:16:24.359 --> 00:16:25.360
- Ah, ndio? - Ndiyo.

00:16:25.444 --> 00:16:27.988
Naam, nilionekana bora kuliko mke wako nilipomwacha asubuhi ya leo.

00:16:29.156 --> 00:16:30.699
Ulipokuwa ukinywa au kulala,

00:16:30.782 --> 00:16:33.744
au chochote kile ulichokiona kuwa muhimu sana Jumatatu asubuhi,

00:16:33.827 --> 00:16:34.828
Phil Larson alipiga simu.

00:16:34.912 --> 00:16:37.581
Alisema watoto wengine wanaiba gnomes kutoka bustani yake tena.

00:16:37.664 --> 00:16:39.124
Loo, wale gnome wa bustani tena.

00:16:39.208 --> 00:16:41.460
Naam, nitakuambia nini, nitafanya hivyo moja kwa moja.

00:16:41.543 --> 00:16:43.086
Kuhusu jambo muhimu zaidi,

00:16:43.170 --> 00:16:45.214
Joyce Byers hawezi kumpata mwanawe asubuhi ya leo.

00:16:45.297 --> 00:16:48.050
Mmm. Sawa, nitazungumzia hilo.

00:16:48.133 --> 00:16:50.344
-Nipe dakika moja tu. -Joyce amekasirika sana.

00:16:50.427 --> 00:16:52.304
Naam, Flo, Flo, tumejadili hili.

00:16:52.387 --> 00:16:54.723
Asubuhi ni kwa ajili ya kahawa na kutafakari.

00:16:54.806 --> 00:16:58.685
-Mkuu, tayari yuko ndani yako-- -Kahawa na tafakari, Flo!

00:17:09.154 --> 00:17:11.949
Nimekuwa nikisubiri hapa zaidi ya saa moja, Hopper.

00:17:12.032 --> 00:17:14.618
Na ninaomba msamaha tena.

00:17:14.701 --> 00:17:16.078
Ninapoteza fahamu!

00:17:16.161 --> 00:17:19.748
Angalia, kijana wa umri wake, labda anacheza tu kama mlevi, sawa?

00:17:19.831 --> 00:17:21.833
Hapana, si Wosia wangu. Yeye si kama hivyo.

00:17:21.917 --> 00:17:23.460
-Asingefanya hivyo. -Naam, huwezi kujua.

00:17:23.544 --> 00:17:25.254
Namaanisha, mama yangu alidhani nilikuwa kwenye timu ya mjadala,

00:17:25.337 --> 00:17:26.922
wakati kweli nilikuwa nikimkosea Chrissy Carpenter tu

00:17:27.005 --> 00:17:28.674
nyuma ya Oldsmobile ya baba yangu, kwa hivyo...

00:17:28.757 --> 00:17:31.718
Tazama, yeye si kama wewe, Hopper. Yeye si kama mimi.

00:17:31.802 --> 00:17:34.304
Yeye si kama... wengi.

00:17:34.388 --> 00:17:38.267
Ana marafiki kadhaa, lakini, unajua, watoto, ni wakorofi.

00:17:38.350 --> 00:17:40.185
Wanamdhihaki. Wanamwita majina.

00:17:40.269 --> 00:17:42.312
-Wanamcheka, nguo zake -- -Nguo zake?

00:17:42.396 --> 00:17:44.356
-Kuna tatizo gani na nguo zake? -Sijui.

00:17:44.439 --> 00:17:46.733
-Je, hilo lina maana? -Labda.

00:17:46.817 --> 00:17:49.861
Tazama, yeye ni... Ni mtoto mwenye hisia nyeti.

00:17:49.945 --> 00:17:53.657
Lonnie... Lonnie alikuwa akisema alikuwa mlaghai.

00:17:53.740 --> 00:17:55.075
Alimwita mchawi.

00:17:55.158 --> 00:17:59.079
-Je, yeye? -Anakosa kile alicho.

00:18:00.581 --> 00:18:02.958
Mara ya mwisho ulisikia kutoka kwa Lonnie ilikuwa lini?

00:18:05.085 --> 00:18:09.423
Uh, mara ya mwisho nilisikia, alikuwa Indianapolis. Hiyo ilikuwa yapata mwaka mmoja uliopita.

00:18:09.506 --> 00:18:12.259
-Lakini hana uhusiano wowote na hili. -Kwa nini usinipe namba yake?

00:18:12.342 --> 00:18:14.219
Unajua, Hopper, hana uhusiano wowote na hili. Niamini.

00:18:14.303 --> 00:18:17.514
Joyce, mara 99 kati ya 100, mtoto anapotea,

00:18:17.598 --> 00:18:19.725
mtoto yuko na mzazi au jamaa.

00:18:19.808 --> 00:18:21.310
Vipi kuhusu wakati mwingine?

00:18:21.393 --> 00:18:24.730
-Nini? -Ulisema, "99 kati ya 100."

00:18:24.855 --> 00:18:26.857
-Vipi kuhusu wakati mwingine, ule mmoja? -Joyce.

00:18:26.940 --> 00:18:28.066
Yule!

00:18:28.150 --> 00:18:29.985
- Joyce, huyu ni Hawkins, sawa?

00:18:30.068 --> 00:18:31.820
Unataka kujua jambo baya zaidi kuwahi kutokea hapa

00:18:31.903 --> 00:18:32.988
katika miaka minne niliyokuwa nikifanya kazi hapa?

00:18:33.071 --> 00:18:34.239
Unataka kujua jambo baya zaidi?

00:18:34.323 --> 00:18:37.451
Ilikuwa wakati bundi aliposhambulia kichwa cha Eleanor Gillespie

00:18:37.534 --> 00:18:39.244
kwa sababu ilidhani kwamba nywele zake zilikuwa kiota.

00:18:39.328 --> 00:18:41.997
Sawa, sawa. Nitampigia simu Lonnie.

00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:43.790
Atazungumza nami kabla hajazungumza na--

00:18:43.874 --> 00:18:45.834
-Nini, nguruwe? -Polisi!

00:18:46.918 --> 00:18:49.921
Mtafute tu mwanangu, Hop.

00:18:50.005 --> 00:18:51.882
Mtafute!

00:19:03.477 --> 00:19:04.645
Dkt. Brenner.

00:19:06.605 --> 00:19:08.273
Kwa njia hii, waungwana.

00:19:08.357 --> 00:19:11.193
Bawa lote la mashariki litaondolewa ndani ya saa moja.

00:19:11.276 --> 00:19:15.113
Tumefunga eneo hili kufuatia itifaki ya karantini.

00:21:01.303 --> 00:21:03.930
- Hapa ndipo ilipotoka? - Ndiyo.

00:21:04.014 --> 00:21:05.015
Na msichana?

00:21:06.641 --> 00:21:08.769
Hawezi kwenda mbali.

00:22:02.030 --> 00:22:03.740
Sawa, na moja zaidi.

00:22:04.699 --> 00:22:06.618
Habari, Ben. Una maoni gani kuhusu hilo, uh...

00:22:06.701 --> 00:22:08.245
Haya, sijui. Sijui.

00:22:08.328 --> 00:22:10.664
Sijui, wastani wa pointi 37 kwa kila mchezo--

00:22:10.747 --> 00:22:12.457
- Thelathini na saba sasa, lakini... - Bw. Basket.

00:22:42.612 --> 00:22:44.114
Habari!

00:22:44.197 --> 00:22:45.323
Njoo hapa!

00:22:46.074 --> 00:22:47.367
Haya, njoo hapa!

00:22:52.038 --> 00:22:54.082
Unafikiri unaweza kuniibia, kijana?

00:22:56.585 --> 00:22:57.752
Nini huko kuzimu?

00:22:59.296 --> 00:23:02.132
--Kumbuka, maliza sura ya 12

00:23:02.215 --> 00:23:06.011
na jibu 12.3 kuhusu tofauti kati ya jaribio

00:23:06.094 --> 00:23:08.221
na aina zingine za uchunguzi wa kisayansi.

00:23:08.305 --> 00:23:12.183
Hii itakuwa kwenye jaribio, ambalo litashughulikia sura ya 10 hadi 12.

00:23:12.267 --> 00:23:15.312
Itakuwa chaguo nyingi ukiwa na sehemu ya insha.

00:23:16.980 --> 00:23:18.356
Kwa hivyo, ilikuja?

00:23:18.440 --> 00:23:19.816
Samahani, wavulana.

00:23:19.899 --> 00:23:21.776
Nachukia kuwa mtoa habari mbaya, lakini...

00:23:22.986 --> 00:23:23.903
ilikuja.

00:23:27.490 --> 00:23:28.491
Ndiyo!

00:23:28.575 --> 00:23:30.368
Kibanda cha ham cha Heathkit.

00:23:30.452 --> 00:23:31.911
- Lo! - Je, yeye si mrembo?

00:23:31.995 --> 00:23:34.039
Naamini unaweza kuzungumza na New York kuhusu jambo hili.

00:23:34.122 --> 00:23:35.290
Fikiria kubwa zaidi.

00:23:35.373 --> 00:23:37.375
-California? -Kubwa zaidi.

00:23:37.459 --> 00:23:38.835
Australia?

00:23:39.794 --> 00:23:41.379
--Loo, jamani!

00:23:41.463 --> 00:23:44.341
Will atakapoona hili, ataharibu kabisa.

00:23:44.424 --> 00:23:45.508
Lucas!

00:23:45.592 --> 00:23:46.968
- Samahani.

00:23:49.512 --> 00:23:51.931
Habari, huyu ni Mike Wheeler,

00:23:52.015 --> 00:23:54.726
rais wa Hawkins Middle AV Club.

00:23:56.269 --> 00:23:57.479
Unafanya nini?

00:23:57.562 --> 00:23:58.730
Habari, huyu ni Dustin,

00:23:58.813 --> 00:24:01.816
na huyu ndiye katibu na mweka hazina wa Hawkins Middle AV Club.

00:24:01.900 --> 00:24:04.069
Je, unakula kangaruu kwa kifungua kinywa?

00:24:06.237 --> 00:24:11.076
Samahani kuingilia kati, lakini, uh, naweza kuazima Michael, Lucas na Dustin?

00:24:16.081 --> 00:24:17.624
Sawa, sawa, sawa.

00:24:17.707 --> 00:24:20.669
Mmoja baada ya mwingine, sawa? Wewe.

00:24:21.628 --> 00:24:23.380
-Ulisema anachukua nini? -Mirkwood.

00:24:23.463 --> 00:24:26.049
-Mirkwood? -Ndiyo.

00:24:26.132 --> 00:24:29.636
-Je, umewahi kusikia kuhusu Mirkwood? -Sijawahi kusikia. Hilo linasikika kama la kubuniwa kwangu.

00:24:29.719 --> 00:24:31.513
Hapana, ni kutoka kwa Bwana wa Pete.

00:24:31.596 --> 00:24:34.474
-Naam, Hobbit. -Haijalishi.

00:24:34.557 --> 00:24:36.393
- Aliuliza! - "Aliuliza!"

00:24:36.476 --> 00:24:38.061
- Nyamazeni, jamani! - Hei, hei, hei!

00:24:38.186 --> 00:24:40.105
-Nimesema nini? -Nyamaza.

00:24:40.188 --> 00:24:43.483
Mmoja baada ya mwingine. Wewe.

00:24:43.566 --> 00:24:46.778
Mirkwood, ni barabara halisi. Ni jina tu lililobuniwa.

00:24:46.861 --> 00:24:48.238
Ni pale Cornwallis na Kerley wanapokutana.

00:24:48.321 --> 00:24:50.824
-Ndiyo, sawa, nadhani najua hilo-- -Tunaweza kukuonyesha, ukitaka.

00:24:50.907 --> 00:24:52.242
Nilisema kwamba najua!

00:24:52.325 --> 00:24:54.244
-Tunaweza kusaidia kuangalia. -Ndiyo.

00:24:54.327 --> 00:24:56.246
- Hapana.

00:24:56.329 --> 00:24:59.457
Hapana. Baada ya shule, nyote mtarudi nyumbani.

00:24:59.541 --> 00:25:00.750
Mara moja.

00:25:00.834 --> 00:25:04.629
Hiyo ina maana kwamba hakuna kuendesha baiskeli huku na huko kumtafuta rafiki yako, hakuna uchunguzi,

00:25:04.713 --> 00:25:05.797
hakuna upuuzi.

00:25:05.880 --> 00:25:07.841
Hiki si kitabu cha Bwana wa Pete.

00:25:07.924 --> 00:25:10.719
-Hobbit. -Nyamaza!

00:25:10.802 --> 00:25:12.178
- Haya! - Acha!

00:25:13.471 --> 00:25:15.390
Je, ninajiweka wazi?

00:25:20.603 --> 00:25:25.150
Je, ninajiweka wazi...?

00:25:26.151 --> 00:25:27.944
- Ndiyo, bwana. - Ndiyo.

00:25:39.789 --> 00:25:41.499
Piga-piga-piga-piga!

00:25:41.583 --> 00:25:43.293
Kuna mtu yeyote nyumbani?

00:25:43.376 --> 00:25:45.003
Nenosiri?

00:25:45.086 --> 00:25:47.046
Loo, Rada...

00:25:48.381 --> 00:25:50.884
Kutoka barabarani-- Kutoka barabarani?

00:25:50.967 --> 00:25:53.386
Ndiyo. Unaweza kuingia.

00:25:53.470 --> 00:25:55.930
Asante, bwana.

00:25:56.931 --> 00:25:58.558
Kwa hivyo, nadhani nini?

00:25:58.641 --> 00:26:01.102
Niliondoka mapema na...

00:26:01.186 --> 00:26:03.855
Ta-da! Mchawi wa poltergeist.

00:26:03.938 --> 00:26:05.482
Mimi... nilidhani sikuruhusiwa kuiona.

00:26:05.565 --> 00:26:06.941
Nilibadilisha mawazo yangu.

00:26:07.984 --> 00:26:09.819
Ilimradi huna ndoto mbaya kwa wiki nzima.

00:26:09.903 --> 00:26:12.405
Hapana, sitaogopa. Siogopi tena hivyo.

00:26:12.489 --> 00:26:13.490
Loo, ndio?

00:26:13.573 --> 00:26:15.241
Hata si wa wacheshi?

00:26:15.325 --> 00:26:16.409
Hapana.

00:26:16.493 --> 00:26:18.870
Vipi kuhusu mchawi wangu?

00:26:18.953 --> 00:26:20.371
-Hapana. Mama... -Ooh...

00:26:20.455 --> 00:26:22.290
-Sina umri wa miaka mitano tena. -Lakini Will Byers...

00:26:22.373 --> 00:26:24.834
-Nitakupikia chakula changu -- -Simama. Huo ni ujinga sana. Mama!

00:26:29.172 --> 00:26:30.298
Je, atakufa?

00:26:30.381 --> 00:26:31.966
- Je, ni mapenzi? - Je, ni mapenzi?

00:26:33.510 --> 00:26:34.761
Je, atakufa?

00:26:37.722 --> 00:26:39.307
-Je, utapenda? -Je, utapenda!

00:26:40.642 --> 00:26:42.101
- Je! - Je?

00:26:42.185 --> 00:26:43.728
Je, utapenda!

00:26:43.812 --> 00:26:45.480
Uko wapi?

00:26:54.864 --> 00:26:56.074
Wazee.

00:26:56.950 --> 00:26:58.701
Wazazi wako wamesahau kukulisha?

00:27:02.372 --> 00:27:04.207
Je, hiyo ndiyo sababu ulikimbia?

00:27:07.669 --> 00:27:08.878
Wao, uh...

00:27:09.879 --> 00:27:11.047
Walikuumiza?

00:27:13.925 --> 00:27:15.635
Ulikwenda hospitalini, ukaogopa,

00:27:15.718 --> 00:27:17.387
Ulikimbia, uliishia hapa, sivyo?

00:27:20.431 --> 00:27:21.641
Sawa.

00:27:23.476 --> 00:27:26.855
Nitarudisha hii, sawa? Na unaweza kupata kiasi unachotaka.

00:27:27.522 --> 00:27:28.940
Sawa? Labda hata aiskrimu.

00:27:29.023 --> 00:27:31.109
Lakini lazima ujibu maswali yangu machache kwanza, sawa?

00:27:32.569 --> 00:27:34.445
Tumepata ofa?

00:27:36.322 --> 00:27:40.076
Sawa, tuanze na mambo rahisi. Sawa?

00:27:40.159 --> 00:27:43.538
Jina langu ni Benny. Benny Hammond.

00:27:43.621 --> 00:27:45.331
Unaona? Kama hii. Hapa.

00:27:45.415 --> 00:27:48.334
Nimekuelewa. Usijali. Ni sawa.

00:27:48.418 --> 00:27:51.880
Nimefurahi kukutana nawe, ndio. Na wewe ni hivyo?

00:28:01.222 --> 00:28:02.265
Kumi na moja?

00:28:03.308 --> 00:28:04.601
Hiyo ina maana gani?

00:28:05.476 --> 00:28:07.228
Inamaanisha nini?

00:28:08.313 --> 00:28:10.565
-Hapana. -Naam, nitahukumiwa.

00:28:10.648 --> 00:28:12.358
Anazungumza.

00:28:12.442 --> 00:28:14.110
"Hapana"? Hapana, nini?

00:28:15.820 --> 00:28:18.907
Sawa. Nadhani hakuna chakula zaidi, basi.

00:28:18.990 --> 00:28:20.158
Kumi na moja.

00:28:21.534 --> 00:28:22.577
Ndiyo.

00:28:23.912 --> 00:28:25.455
Inamaanisha nini?

00:28:27.206 --> 00:28:28.625
Kumi na moja.

00:28:30.335 --> 00:28:32.503
Sawa, basi.

00:28:32.587 --> 00:28:34.339
Haya basi.

00:28:34.422 --> 00:28:36.174
Pumzika, jipe ​​raha.

00:28:38.551 --> 00:28:41.179
Ndiyo, tazama, ninachojua ni kwamba anaogopa sana.

00:28:41.262 --> 00:28:43.389
Ndiyo, nadhani labda ametendewa vibaya au...

00:28:43.473 --> 00:28:45.099
kutekwa nyara au kitu kama hicho.

00:28:46.601 --> 00:28:49.187
Ndiyo, itakuwa vizuri kama mtu angekuja.

00:28:49.270 --> 00:28:53.733
Ndiyo, tuko 4819 Randolph Lane. Ndiyo, Randolph.

00:29:20.635 --> 00:29:22.387
Will Byers?

00:29:25.181 --> 00:29:26.557
Je, utapenda!

00:29:27.809 --> 00:29:30.061
Will Byers?

00:29:33.064 --> 00:29:35.066
Njoo, mtoto!

00:29:35.149 --> 00:29:36.401
Je, atakufa?

00:29:37.527 --> 00:29:41.322
--Hei! Nina kitu.

00:29:48.371 --> 00:29:51.291
-Hiyo baiskeli yake? -Ndiyo, lazima awe ameanguka.

00:29:52.583 --> 00:29:54.210
Unafikiri aliumia wakati wa vuli?

00:29:55.086 --> 00:29:56.629
Hakuumia sana kiasi kwamba hakuweza kuondoka.

00:29:56.713 --> 00:29:58.631
Baiskeli kama hii ni kama Cadillac kwa watoto hawa.

00:29:58.715 --> 00:30:00.341
Angetembea nayo hadi nyumbani.

00:30:11.352 --> 00:30:12.312
...acha kazi ikiwa nitashinda.

00:30:12.395 --> 00:30:14.063
Loo, Ijumaa natakiwa...

00:30:14.147 --> 00:30:16.941
...lakini tutalipa uharibifu wowote utakaotokea kwa mali yako.

00:30:17.025 --> 00:30:18.693
- Ni kweli tu, um... - Hiyo ni hakika.

00:30:28.036 --> 00:30:29.203
Je, Lonnie yupo?

00:30:29.287 --> 00:30:31.581
- Lonnie hayupo hapa kwa sasa. - Tafadhali unaweza--

00:30:31.664 --> 00:30:33.541
-Nilikuambia, Lonnie hayupo. -Huyu ni nani?

00:30:33.624 --> 00:30:35.626
-Mpenzi wake, Cynthia. -Cynthia.

00:30:35.710 --> 00:30:38.421
-Huyu ni nani jamani? -Cynthia, huyu ni Joyce.

00:30:38.504 --> 00:30:40.256
-Nani? -Mke wa zamani wa Lonnie.

00:30:40.340 --> 00:30:42.383
-Ninahitaji sana kuzungumza naye-- -Lonnie hayupo.

00:30:42.467 --> 00:30:44.344
-Tafadhali unaweza kuweka-- Hapana! -Kwa nini usipige simu tena baadaye?

00:30:44.427 --> 00:30:45.636
Hapana, si baadaye. Sasa!

00:30:45.720 --> 00:30:46.888
- Inaweza--

00:30:46.971 --> 00:30:48.389
- Mpenzi! - Mama.

00:30:48.473 --> 00:30:50.933
-Nini? -Lazima utulie.

00:30:59.692 --> 00:31:00.735
Haya, umemfikia Lonnie.

00:31:00.818 --> 00:31:03.029
Acha ujumbe nami nitakupigia kelele mara moja.

00:31:03.112 --> 00:31:06.866
Lonnie, kijana mmoja alinipigia simu.

00:31:06.949 --> 00:31:09.452
Will hayupo. Sijui yuko wapi.

00:31:09.535 --> 00:31:10.703
Nahitaji...

00:31:10.787 --> 00:31:13.373
Nahitaji tu unipigie simu tena, tafadhali, tu--

00:31:16.042 --> 00:31:17.794
- Laana! Laana!

00:31:17.877 --> 00:31:19.545
--Mama?

00:31:19.629 --> 00:31:20.630
Nini?

00:31:22.673 --> 00:31:23.841
Polisi.

00:31:38.689 --> 00:31:42.235
-Ilikuwa imelala tu hapo? -Ndiyo. Cal?

00:31:43.152 --> 00:31:46.823
-Je, ilikuwa na damu yoyote juu yake, au-- -Hapana, hapana, hapana, hapana, hapana...

00:31:46.906 --> 00:31:48.408
Phil?

00:31:48.491 --> 00:31:50.910
Kama umepata baiskeli huko nje, kwa nini uko hapa?

00:31:51.953 --> 00:31:54.831
- Naam, alikuwa na ufunguo wa nyumba, sivyo? - Ndiyo.

00:31:55.832 --> 00:31:57.250
Kwa hivyo...

00:31:58.209 --> 00:31:59.377
labda alirudi nyumbani.

00:31:59.460 --> 00:32:01.504
Unafikiri sikuangalia nyumba yangu mwenyewe?

00:32:01.587 --> 00:32:03.381
Sisemi hivyo.

00:32:04.298 --> 00:32:07.051
- Je, hii imekuwa hapa kila wakati? - Nini? Sijui.

00:32:07.135 --> 00:32:09.971
Labda. Namaanisha, nina wavulana wawili. Tazama mahali hapa.

00:32:11.597 --> 00:32:12.765
Huna uhakika?

00:32:24.735 --> 00:32:25.736
Habari.

00:32:27.280 --> 00:32:29.115
Haya, kuna nini na huyu jamaa, sivyo?

00:32:29.198 --> 00:32:31.701
Hakuna, labda ana njaa tu. Haya.

00:33:50.655 --> 00:33:52.323
- Hujambo! - Yesu!

00:33:52.406 --> 00:33:54.992
Wewe ni nini, kiziwi? Nimekuwa nikikuita.

00:33:55.076 --> 00:33:57.537
--Kuna nini kinaendelea?

00:33:59.705 --> 00:34:00.831
Habari?

00:34:00.915 --> 00:34:04.001
-Una uhakika uko sawa, Mkuu? -Sikiliza, nataka umpigie simu Flo.

00:34:04.085 --> 00:34:05.419
Nataka kupanga kikundi cha utafutaji, sawa?

00:34:05.503 --> 00:34:08.631
Wajitolea wote anaoweza kuwakusanya. Lete tochi pia.

00:34:08.714 --> 00:34:11.008
Unadhani tuna tatizo hapa?

00:34:18.057 --> 00:34:20.810
Tunapaswa kuwa huko nje sasa hivi. Tunapaswa kusaidia kumtafuta.

00:34:20.893 --> 00:34:22.770
Tumepitia hili, Mike. Mkuu anasema--

00:34:22.853 --> 00:34:24.355
-Sijali mkuu alisema nini. -Michael!

00:34:24.438 --> 00:34:26.107
Tunapaswa kufanya jambo. Will anaweza kuwa hatarini.

00:34:26.190 --> 00:34:27.400
Sababu zaidi ya kubaki hapo.

00:34:27.483 --> 00:34:29.527
-Mama! -Mwisho wa majadiliano.

00:34:33.739 --> 00:34:37.660
Kwa hivyo ... mimi na Barbara tutasoma nyumbani kwake usiku wa leo.

00:34:37.743 --> 00:34:40.162
-Hiyo ni nzuri, sivyo? -Hapana, si nzuri.

00:34:40.246 --> 00:34:41.497
Nini? Kwa nini isiwe hivyo?

00:34:41.581 --> 00:34:44.792
Unafikiri kwa nini? Je, ninazungumza Kichina katika nyumba hii?

00:34:44.875 --> 00:34:47.920
Hadi tutakapojua Will yuko sawa, hakuna anayeondoka.

00:34:48.004 --> 00:34:49.797
-Huu ni upuuzi mtupu. -Lugha.

00:34:49.880 --> 00:34:51.299
Kwa hivyo tuko chini ya kizuizi cha nyumbani?

00:34:51.382 --> 00:34:53.301
Kwa sababu tu rafiki yake Mike alipotea njiani kurudi nyumbani kutoka...

00:34:53.384 --> 00:34:55.678
-Subiri, hili ni kosa la Will? -Nancy, rudisha hilo nyuma.

00:34:55.761 --> 00:34:57.305
-Hapana! -Umekasirika tu

00:34:57.388 --> 00:34:59.348
Kwa sababu unataka kukaa na Steve.

00:35:00.975 --> 00:35:02.226
-Steve? -Steve ni nani?

00:35:02.310 --> 00:35:04.729
-Mpenzi wake mpya. -Wewe ni mjanja sana, Mike!

00:35:04.812 --> 00:35:06.606
- Lugha!

00:35:08.274 --> 00:35:09.692
Nancy, rudi.

00:35:10.526 --> 00:35:11.777
Rudi!

00:35:11.861 --> 00:35:15.281
Ni sawa. Ni sawa, Holly. Hapa, kunywa juisi, sawa?

00:35:15.990 --> 00:35:17.033
Unaona, Michael?

00:35:17.116 --> 00:35:19.410
- Unaona kinachotokea? - Nini kinatokea wakati nini?

00:35:19.493 --> 00:35:23.080
Mimi pekee ndiye ninayejifanya kama kawaida hapa! Mimi pekee ndiye ninayemjali Will!

00:35:23.164 --> 00:35:25.207
Hiyo si haki kabisa, mwanangu.

00:35:25.291 --> 00:35:26.500
Tunajali.

00:35:31.380 --> 00:35:33.174
-Mike! -Mwache aende zake.

00:35:35.885 --> 00:35:38.304
Natumai unafurahia kuku wako, Ted.

00:35:39.055 --> 00:35:40.598
Nilifanya nini?

00:35:42.933 --> 00:35:45.519
Halo! Nilifanya nini?

00:35:48.564 --> 00:35:50.608
- Will! - Will Byers!

00:35:50.691 --> 00:35:51.734
Je, utapenda!

00:35:51.817 --> 00:35:53.653
Will, tuko hapa kwa ajili yako, rafiki!

00:35:56.530 --> 00:35:58.741
Yeye ni mwanafunzi mzuri.

00:35:58.824 --> 00:36:02.244
- Nini? - Will. Ni mwanafunzi mzuri.

00:36:02.328 --> 00:36:03.954
Kubwa sana, kwa kweli.

00:36:04.455 --> 00:36:06.374
Sidhani kama tumekutana. Scott Clarke.

00:36:06.457 --> 00:36:09.752
Mwalimu, Hawkins Middle. Dunia na biolojia.

00:36:09.835 --> 00:36:11.837
Siku zote nilikuwa na chuki na sayansi.

00:36:11.921 --> 00:36:13.881
Labda ulikuwa na mwalimu mbaya.

00:36:13.964 --> 00:36:16.300
Ndiyo, Bi. Ratliff alikuwa kazi ya ziada.

00:36:16.384 --> 00:36:19.011
Ratliff? Unaweka dau.

00:36:19.095 --> 00:36:21.263
Bado anapiga teke huku na huko, amini usiamini.

00:36:21.347 --> 00:36:25.142
Loo, naamini. Mama hawafi kamwe, kwa hivyo wananiambia.

00:36:25.768 --> 00:36:27.269
Sarah, binti yangu...

00:36:28.646 --> 00:36:32.817
Galaksi, ulimwengu, chochote kile... Siku zote alielewa mambo hayo yote.

00:36:32.900 --> 00:36:35.361
Siku zote nilidhani kulikuwa na mambo ya kutosha yanayoendelea hapa chini,

00:36:35.444 --> 00:36:37.196
Sikuhitaji kutafuta mahali pengine.

00:36:37.738 --> 00:36:39.490
Binti yako, ana daraja gani?

00:36:39.573 --> 00:36:42.368
-Labda nitampeleka darasani mwangu. -Hapana, yeye, uh...

00:36:42.451 --> 00:36:44.995
Anaishi na mama yake mjini.

00:36:45.079 --> 00:36:48.541
Asante kwa kujitokeza, Teach. Tunashukuru sana.

00:36:50.751 --> 00:36:53.629
-Alifariki miaka michache iliyopita. -Samahani?

00:36:53.713 --> 00:36:54.964
Mtoto wake.

00:37:07.435 --> 00:37:08.978
Lucas, unaiga? Ni Mike.

00:37:09.061 --> 00:37:11.897
-Lucas? -Hei, ni Lucas.

00:37:11.981 --> 00:37:12.982
Najua ni wewe.

00:37:13.065 --> 00:37:16.235
Na sema "juu" unapomaliza kuzungumza ili nijue unapomaliza.

00:37:16.318 --> 00:37:17.945
Nimemaliza. Nimemaliza.

00:37:18.028 --> 00:37:20.448
Nina wasiwasi kuhusu Will. Imekwisha.

00:37:20.531 --> 00:37:22.575
Ndiyo.

00:37:24.410 --> 00:37:26.328
Hii ni ya kichaa. Imeisha.

00:37:26.412 --> 00:37:28.038
Nilikuwa nikifikiria...

00:37:29.540 --> 00:37:32.376
Will angeweza kumtupia Protection jana usiku, lakini hakufanya hivyo.

00:37:32.460 --> 00:37:33.461
Alirusha mpira wa moto.

00:37:33.544 --> 00:37:37.298
-Kupita. -Unamaanisha nini? Kupita.

00:37:37.381 --> 00:37:42.094
Hoja yangu ni kwamba... angeweza kucheza salama, lakini hakufanya hivyo.

00:37:42.178 --> 00:37:44.054
Alijiweka katika hatari ya kukisaidia chama.

00:37:44.138 --> 00:37:45.264
Juu.

00:37:48.058 --> 00:37:50.478
Tukutane katika kumi. Mara kwa mara.

00:38:21.300 --> 00:38:22.301
Unafanya nini hapa?

00:38:22.384 --> 00:38:24.678
Nilikuambia kwenye simu, niko chini ya kifungo cha nyumbani sasa.

00:38:24.762 --> 00:38:27.598
-Nilidhani tungesoma hapa tu. -Hapana. Hakuna njia.

00:38:27.681 --> 00:38:29.934
Loo, njoo. Siwezi kukufanya ushindwe mtihani huu.

00:38:30.017 --> 00:38:31.811
Kwa hivyo tu... vumilia.

00:38:34.855 --> 00:38:35.856
Nilikuambia nini?

00:38:37.274 --> 00:38:38.400
Ninja.

00:38:52.456 --> 00:38:53.916
Unapenda aiskrimu hiyo, sivyo?

00:38:55.167 --> 00:38:56.585
Tabasamu linakupendeza.

00:38:57.419 --> 00:38:59.004
Unajua, tabasamu?

00:39:08.013 --> 00:39:09.765
Sawa. Kaa tu vizuri.

00:39:09.849 --> 00:39:13.227
Yeyote yule, nitawaambia waondoke haraka sana, sawa?

00:39:15.437 --> 00:39:18.107
--Ndiyo, ndiyo, ndiyo...

00:39:19.233 --> 00:39:21.735
-Hei, naweza kukusaidia? -Hujambo, lazima uwe Benny Hammond.

00:39:21.819 --> 00:39:24.071
Ninaogopa nimefungwa. Ninaogopa pia tumefungwa kwa jioni.

00:39:24.154 --> 00:39:26.907
-Kwa hivyo jaribu tena kesho asubuhi. -Connie Frazier. Huduma za Kijamii.

00:39:26.991 --> 00:39:29.869
Ah, Huduma za Kijamii. Samahani. Sikukutarajia hivi karibuni.

00:39:29.952 --> 00:39:32.788
-Hilo ni jambo gumu sana kuendesha gari. -Sio jambo baya sana wakati huu wa usiku.

00:39:32.872 --> 00:39:35.124
Sikiliza, mimi... Sijamwambia kwamba unakuja bado.

00:39:35.207 --> 00:39:39.169
Sikutaka aondoke tena. Ni mjinga kidogo.

00:39:39.253 --> 00:39:41.881
-Watoto ninaofanya nao kazi kwa kawaida huwa. -Sawa, sawa.

00:39:42.464 --> 00:39:45.301
-Kwa hivyo, yuko wapi? -Sawa. Yuko jikoni.

00:39:45.384 --> 00:39:47.219
-Njoo huku. Nitakutambulisha. -Asante.

00:39:47.303 --> 00:39:49.096
Samahani tena kwa kujaribu kukuzuia huko.

00:39:49.179 --> 00:39:50.222
-Ni sawa. -Unajua, ni jambo la kuchekesha.

00:39:50.306 --> 00:39:52.725
- Sauti yako, uh, inasikika tofauti kwenye--

00:40:23.547 --> 00:40:26.467
Ah, jamani. Hii ndiyo yote.

00:40:35.225 --> 00:40:37.061
Halo, jamani. Mnahisi hivyo?

00:40:40.105 --> 00:40:41.774
-Nadhani labda tunapaswa kurudi nyuma. -Hapana.

00:40:41.857 --> 00:40:44.485
Haturudi nyuma. Kaa karibu tu.

00:40:44.568 --> 00:40:45.694
Njoo.

00:40:46.820 --> 00:40:50.157
Baki tu kwenye chaneli sita. Usifanye jambo lolote la kijinga.

00:40:54.828 --> 00:40:56.163
Halo, jamani, subirini.

00:40:56.705 --> 00:40:58.123
Subiri!

00:41:04.004 --> 00:41:06.799
"Ni polima gani zinazotokea kiasili?"

00:41:08.217 --> 00:41:10.678
Wanga na selulosi.

00:41:10.761 --> 00:41:12.012
Mmmh.

00:41:12.096 --> 00:41:16.350
"Katika molekuli ya CH4, atomi za hidrojeni huelekezwa anga

00:41:16.433 --> 00:41:18.894
-kuelekea vituo vya --" -Tetrahedroni.

00:41:18.978 --> 00:41:21.480
Wow. Yesu, umetengeneza ngapi kati ya hizi?

00:41:21.563 --> 00:41:23.399
Ulisema unataka kusaidia.

00:41:24.441 --> 00:41:25.651
Vipi kuhusu hili? Vipi kuhusu...

00:41:25.734 --> 00:41:27.277
Vipi kuhusu kila wakati unapopata kitu sahihi,

00:41:27.361 --> 00:41:28.862
Lazima nivue nguo.

00:41:28.946 --> 00:41:30.531
Lakini kila wakati unapofanya kitu kibaya--

00:41:30.614 --> 00:41:31.824
-Uh, pita. -Oh, njoo.

00:41:31.907 --> 00:41:32.950
-Njoo. -Hapana.

00:41:33.033 --> 00:41:34.410
-Njoo. Itakuwa ya kufurahisha. -Hapana.

00:41:34.493 --> 00:41:35.869
"Wakati wa kunereka kwa sehemu,

00:41:35.953 --> 00:41:38.622
hidrokaboni hutenganishwa kulingana na--"

00:41:38.706 --> 00:41:39.748
Kiwango cha kuyeyuka.

00:41:41.208 --> 00:41:43.377
Loo, ni kiwango cha kuchemka.

00:41:43.460 --> 00:41:44.878
Hiyo ndiyo niliyomaanisha.

00:41:44.962 --> 00:41:46.964
Ndiyo, sivyo ulivyosema.

00:41:47.881 --> 00:41:49.675
-Hapana hapana?

00:41:50.551 --> 00:41:52.886
Loo, unahitaji... Je, unahitaji msaada, au...

00:41:52.970 --> 00:41:54.013
Hapana.

00:42:15.534 --> 00:42:17.161
Steve. Steve, njoo.

00:42:17.244 --> 00:42:18.245
Nini?

00:42:18.328 --> 00:42:20.456
Je, wewe ni mwendawazimu? Wazazi wangu wako hapa.

00:42:22.166 --> 00:42:24.668
Hilo ni jambo la ajabu, mimi... siwaoni.

00:42:28.505 --> 00:42:33.177
Je, huu ulikuwa mpango wako tangu mwanzo? Ili... kuingia chumbani kwangu kisha...

00:42:33.260 --> 00:42:35.846
-pata nafasi nyingine kwenye mkanda wako. -Hapana. Nancy, hapana.

00:42:35.929 --> 00:42:38.057
Mimi si Laurie, au Amy, au Becky.

00:42:38.140 --> 00:42:39.725
Unamaanisha, wewe si mlaghai.

00:42:40.559 --> 00:42:41.643
Sio hivyo ninavyosema.

00:42:41.727 --> 00:42:43.479
Unajua, wewe ni mrembo sana unaposema uongo.

00:42:43.979 --> 00:42:45.230
Nyamaza.

00:42:48.108 --> 00:42:49.485
Steve mbaya.

00:42:49.568 --> 00:42:53.113
Mbaya. Usimfanyie hivyo Bi. Nancy...

00:42:53.697 --> 00:42:55.741
Wewe ni mjinga, Steve Harrington.

00:42:56.658 --> 00:42:58.702
Wewe ni mrembo, Nancy Wheeler.

00:43:05.125 --> 00:43:07.711
"Ikilinganishwa na kiwango cha athari zisizo za kikaboni,

00:43:07.795 --> 00:43:11.548
kiwango cha athari za kikaboni kwa ujumla ni..."

00:43:14.551 --> 00:43:17.596
Jonathan, wow. Umechukua hizi?

00:43:18.514 --> 00:43:20.015
Hizi ni nzuri sana.

00:43:21.141 --> 00:43:24.103
Loo, kweli wapo.

00:43:25.270 --> 00:43:28.357
- Najua sijafika huko kwa ajili yako. - Nimekuwa...

00:43:28.440 --> 00:43:30.526
nikifanya kazi kwa bidii sana na mimi...

00:43:30.609 --> 00:43:32.444
Najisikia vibaya tu. Hata sijui...

00:43:32.528 --> 00:43:34.988
Sijui kinachoendelea na wewe.

00:43:35.072 --> 00:43:37.825
Sawa? Samahani kuhusu hilo.

00:43:41.203 --> 00:43:42.496
Haya, ni nini?

00:43:43.413 --> 00:43:44.748
Ni nini, mpenzi?

00:43:46.500 --> 00:43:48.919
- Hakuna. - Niambie. Niambie.

00:43:49.002 --> 00:43:51.046
-Njoo. Unaweza... -Hapana.

00:43:51.130 --> 00:43:52.297
Ni tu...

00:43:53.507 --> 00:43:55.300
Nilipaswa kuwa pale kwa ajili yake.

00:43:55.384 --> 00:43:58.387
Hapana. Loo, hapana. Huwezi kujifanyia hivyo.

00:43:58.470 --> 00:44:01.682
Hili halikuwa kosa lako. Unanisikia?

00:44:01.765 --> 00:44:05.435
- Yuko... karibu. - Najua. Mimi...

00:44:06.103 --> 00:44:08.814
Nahisi moyoni mwangu.

00:44:09.565 --> 00:44:12.359
Lazima tu... Lazima uniamini katika hili, sawa?

00:44:15.112 --> 00:44:16.780
-Ndiyo. -Oh, angalia hii.

00:44:16.864 --> 00:44:19.241
Tazama hii. Tazama hii.

00:44:21.577 --> 00:44:23.745
-Namaanisha, ndivyo ilivyo, sivyo? -Ndiyo.

00:44:23.829 --> 00:44:25.622
Hiyo ndiyo. Hiyo ndiyo.

00:44:29.209 --> 00:44:32.129
- Habari?

00:44:32.212 --> 00:44:33.839
- Habari?

00:44:33.922 --> 00:44:34.965
Lonnie?

00:44:35.048 --> 00:44:36.800
-Baba? -Hopper?

00:44:36.884 --> 00:44:38.927
--Huyu ni nani?

00:44:42.222 --> 00:44:43.265
Je, atakufa?

00:44:44.141 --> 00:44:45.225
-Je, ni mapenzi? -Ni mapenzi?

00:44:48.061 --> 00:44:49.438
--Mama, ni Will?

00:44:50.439 --> 00:44:51.857
- Huyu ni nani?

00:44:51.940 --> 00:44:54.067
- Umemfanyia nini kijana wangu? - Nini? Nini?

00:44:54.151 --> 00:44:55.652
Nirudishie mwanangu!

00:44:57.613 --> 00:44:59.448
--Hujambo?

00:44:59.531 --> 00:45:00.782
Habari, huyu ni nani?

00:45:00.866 --> 00:45:03.619
- Habari? Huyu ni nani?

00:45:03.702 --> 00:45:06.163
- Mama, ilikuwa nani? Ilikuwa nani, Mama?

00:45:06.246 --> 00:45:07.915
- Alikuwa yeye. - Niangalie, Mama. Je, ilikuwa ni Mapenzi?

00:45:07.998 --> 00:45:09.207
-Ndiyo. -Alisema nini?

00:45:09.291 --> 00:45:11.418
Alipumua tu. Alipumua tu.

00:45:11.501 --> 00:45:13.462
- Na kulikuwa na mtu mwingine hapo? - Mimi...

00:45:13.545 --> 00:45:16.256
-Mama, nani alikuwepo? Alikuwa nani? -Alikuwa yeye.

00:45:16.340 --> 00:45:19.051
Najua ilikuwa ni pumzi yake. Najua ilikuwa ni pumzi yake.

00:45:20.344 --> 00:45:21.720
--Je, utapenda!

00:45:22.721 --> 00:45:25.223
- Mapenzi! - Kwaheri!

00:45:25.307 --> 00:45:28.060
Nina X-Men 134 yako!

00:45:28.810 --> 00:45:30.896
Jamani, nadhani tunapaswa kurudi nyuma.

00:45:30.979 --> 00:45:32.230
Kweli, Dustin?

00:45:32.314 --> 00:45:34.608
Unataka kuwa mtoto, kisha rudi nyumbani tayari!

00:45:34.691 --> 00:45:36.401
Ninafanya tu ukweli, Lucas!

00:45:36.485 --> 00:45:38.487
Hapana, unakuwa tu dada mkubwa!

00:45:39.112 --> 00:45:42.491
Uliwahi kufikiria Will alipotea kwa sababu alipata kitu kibaya?

00:45:42.574 --> 00:45:45.452
Na tunaenda mahali pale pale alipoonekana mara ya mwisho?

00:45:45.535 --> 00:45:48.372
-Na hatuna silaha au kitu chochote? -Dustin, nyamaza.

00:45:48.455 --> 00:45:50.457
Ninasema tu, je, hilo linaonekana kuwa jambo la busara kwako?

00:45:50.540 --> 00:45:52.668
- Nyamaza. Nyamaza.

00:45:52.751 --> 00:45:54.419
Je, mmesikia hilo?